data.product_title: OPPO Reno7 Pro x League of Legends Mobile Game Jinx Limited Edition Smartphone with 50W Ultra-thin Charger
data.product_description: OPPO Reno7 Pro League of Legends Mobile Game Jinx Limited Edition - limited to 10,000 units globallyAs a limited edition, the configuration of the smartphone is the same as that of the ordinary version which is equipped with a Dimensity 1200-MAX processor. The biggest feature of the limited edition is the various League of Legends mobile game elements.The rear cover takes the black mist of the summoners rift as its main design element, supplemented by three dark streaks, symbolizing the three lanes of League of Legends. At the same time, the diamond-shaped dark streak in the middle symbolizes the honor in the mobile game, while the L logo that shines in the middle of the rear cover is inspired by the demotion shield.League of Legends champion character Jinx served as the inspiration behind the device. The limited edition features a dynamic and customized theme, screen lock, fingerprint unlock and charging animations. Two different themes of Champions and Jinx are available, while the sound effect of Pentakill is one of the phones notification sounds.In addition to the smartphone, a variety of accessories for the limited edition also share many design elements from the League of Legends mobile game series. For example, the sim card pin is designed as Jinxs bullet necklace.In addition to the customized charger and charging cable, the Reno7 Pro Limited Edition also provides a customized smartphone case with Jinx graffiti, and also provides a Jinx smartphone pendant that turns into a Lucky Poro.
